OL,3,CFamily unable to return home after
OL,4,Clandslide severely damaged their house
OL,6,FIt's been over a year since a landslip
OL,7,Fin Cwmtillery severely damaged the
OL,8,FHoneyfield-Connor family's home.
OL,10,FThe landslip at a disused coal tip
OL,11,Foccurred during Storm Bert in November
OL,12,Flast year. Sandbags remain outside the
OL,13,Fdoor as the family unpacks boxes in
OL,14,Ftheir kitchen, which was flooded in
OL,15,Fthe landslide.
OL,17,FDozens in the former mining village
OL,18,Fwere evacuated from their homes
OL,19,Fovernight as mud and water came up to
OL,20,Ftheir windows following the storm.
