OL,6,FInside the end house, Tina's daughter
OL,7,FIsla listened as the coal tip slid
OL,8,Fdown the street.
OL,10,FShe said the noise was similar to that
OL,11,Fheard by those in the Aberfan disaster
OL,12,Fof 1966, when a colliery spoil tip
OL,13,Fcollapsed and engulfed a primary
OL,14,Fschool and surrounding houses.
