OL,6,F"I heard a noise that sounded like a
OL,7,Flow-flying jet. I was only made aware
OL,8,Fafter that night that that's the same
OL,9,Fsound the children at Aberfan had
OL,10,Fheard," she told ITV Cymru Wales'
OL,11,FRural Affairs Correspondent Hannah
OL,12,FThomas.
OL,14,FThe Welsh Government confirmed at the
OL,15,Ftime that it was a landslip caused by
OL,16,Fa "singular wash-out of former coal
OL,17,Ftip in the area."
