OL,6,FThe tip above the Honeyfield-Connors'
OL,7,Fhome was Category D - meaning it had
OL,8,F"potential to impact public safety"
OL,9,Fand need to be inspected at least
OL,10,Ftwice a year.
OL,12,FThere are 2,573 recorded coal tips in
OL,13,FWales, with 368 being Category C and D
OL,14,F- the highest categories of risk - and
OL,15,Fare classed as those with the
OL,16,Fpotential to impact public safety.
