OL,6,FSince that day, around 800,000 homes
OL,7,Fin Wales have been signposted to
OL,8,Fadvice about disused coal tips as the
OL,9,FWelsh Government continues inspecting
OL,10,Fpotentially dangerous sites.
OL,12,FThe new safety and awareness campaign
OL,13,Fcomes after the Disused Mine and
OL,14,FQuarry Tips (Wales) Act passed through
OL,15,Fthe Senedd earlier this year and
OL,16,Freceived Royal Assent in September.
OL,18,FThe Climate Change Secretary Huw
OL,19,FIranca-Davies has been to see the
OL,20,Fwater drainage that was put in place
OL,21,Fto prevent this happening again.
