OL,6,FHowever, he told ITV Cymru Wales that
OL,7,Fhe "can never give a guarantee" that
OL,8,Fanother landslide like Cwmtillery will
OL,9,Fnever happen again.
OL,11,F"We're investing, we've got people on
OL,12,Fthe ground making these tips safe, so
OL,13,Fthat anybody that lives in the shadow
OL,14,Fof these tips, with this industrial
OL,15,Flegacy, can feel reassured that we're
OL,16,Fgetting on with the work for them," he
OL,17,Fsaid.
